snippet.title: PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale E3 Trailer
snippet.description:
PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale is free-for-all brawler featuring the greatest stars in the PlayStation universe!  Check out the E3 trailer for an exclusive look at the two newest All-Stars!

Game website: http://www.playstationallstars.com
Get your copy here: http://bit.ly/MAi90M
